<br>
Sit down with your parents.  Make a deal with them; you'll show them your home work every night.  You'll show them it's done - and then you can play EQ.<br>
<br>
One thing I've learned from when I was young:  You think you can get away with everything...  But people know...  Sooner or later, you'll get caught...  Is it worth getting caught?<br>
<br>
Talk to them - and work out a deal...<br>
